<div id=3D"outline-container-orgdbceec3" class=3D"outline-4">
<h4 id=3D"orgdbceec3">Recipes for the OCaml Cookbook</h4>
<div class=3D"outline-text-4" id=3D"text-orgdbceec3">
<p>
The OCaml Cookbook is a place where OCaml developers share how to solve com=
mon tasks using packages from the ecosystem.
</p>

<p>
A recipe is a code sample and explanations on how to perform a task using a=
 combination of open source libraries.
</p>

<p>
The Cookbook is live at <a href=3D"https://ocaml.org/cookbook">ocaml.org/co=
okbook</a>, but there are not a lot of recipes published yet.
</p>

<p>
When the cookbook was merged, all pull requests to the cookbook branch were=
 automatically closed. We recreated these pull requests and they are ready =
for review.
</p>

<p>
Here's how you can help:
</p>

<ol class=3D"org-ol">
<li>Review <a href=3D"https://github.com/ocaml/ocaml.org/pulls?q=3Dis%3Apr+=
is%3Aopen+label%3ACookbook">open pull requests for cookbook recipes</a>!</l=
i>
<li>Contribute new recipes and tasks for the cookbook!</li>
</ol>

<p>
<b>Relevant PRs and Activities:</b>
</p>
<ul class=3D"org-ul">
<li>PR: Add a checklist for OCaml Cookbook recipe review <a href=3D"https:/=
/github.com/ocaml/ocaml.org/pull/2419">ocaml/ocaml.org#2419</a> by <a href=
=3D"https://github.com/sabine">@sabine</a></li>
