<li>PR: cookbook httpclient <a href=3D"https://github.com/ocaml/ocaml.org/p=
ull/2402">ocaml/ocaml.org#2402</a></li>
<li>PR: cookbook uri <a href=3D"https://github.com/ocaml/ocaml.org/pull/240=
