<div id=3D"outline-container-orgfbb8284" class=3D"outline-4">
<h4 id=3D"orgfbb8284">Community &amp; Marketing Pages Rework</h4>
<div class=3D"outline-text-4" id=3D"text-orgfbb8284">
<p>
This month, we made some progress towards adding videos from the OCaml comm=
unity (e.g., from YouTube and watch.ocaml.org) to the OCaml Planet.
</p>

<p>
Since the size of the OCaml Planet RSS feed grew so large that automation t=
ools (<code>dlvr.it</code>) could no longer process it, we reduced the time=
frame for posts to show up in the RSS feed to the last 90 days.
</p>

<p>
Contributor <a href=3D"https://github.com/ishar19">@ishar19</a> opened a pu=
ll request to add an RSS feed for the Community/Events page. This will allo=
w posting new events to various social media automatically and allow you to=
 subscribe to the Events RSS feed with a RSS reader of your choice.
</p>

<p>
We have <a href=3D"https://www.figma.com/file/7hmoWkQP9PgLTfZCqiZMWa/OCaml-=
Community-Pages?type=3Ddesign&amp;node-id=3D637%3A4539&amp;mode=3Ddesign&am=
p;t=3DRpQlGvOpeg1a93AZ-1">UI designs for the reworked and new pages of the =
community section</a> and we are opening small issues for contributors to h=
elp. :orange_heart:=20
</p>

<p>
<b>Relevant PRs and Activities:</b>
</p>
<ul class=3D"org-ul">
<li>The OCaml Planet
<ul class=3D"org-ul">
<li>PR: Community videos scraping and list page <a href=3D"https://github.c=
om/ocaml/ocaml.org/pull/2441">ocaml/ocaml.org#2441</a> by <a href=3D"https:=
//github.com/cuihtlauac">@cuihtlauac</a></li>
<li>PR: Scrape watch.ocaml.org as an RSS feed <a href=3D"https://github.com=
/ocaml/ocaml.org/pull/2428">ocaml/ocaml.org#2428</a>  by <a href=3D"https:/=
/github.com/cuihtlauac">@cuihtlauac</a></li>
<li>PR: No longer feature posts on the OCaml Planet <a href=3D"https://gith=
ub.com/ocaml/ocaml.org/pull/2430">ocaml/ocaml.org#2430</a> by <a href=3D"ht=
tps://github.com/cuihtlauac">@cuihtlauac</a></li>
<li>PR: Set the cutoff date for the OCaml Planet RSS feed to 90 days <a hre=
f=3D"https://github.com/ocaml/ocaml.org/pull/2416">ocaml/ocaml.org#2416</a>=
  by <a href=3D"https://github.com/sabine">@sabine</a></li>
