<div id=3D"outline-container-org28bdb7d" class=3D"outline-3">
<h3 id=3D"org28bdb7d">Outreachy Internship on Interactive Exercises</h3>
<div class=3D"outline-text-3" id=3D"text-org28bdb7d">
<p>
On May 27, <a href=3D"https://github.com/divyankachaudhari">Divyanka Chaudh=
ari</a> started working with the team, as an Outreachy intern. She's implem=
enting support for running the exercises as a stand-alone project, either i=
n GitHub Codespace, in <code>repl.it</code>, using Jupyter or LearnOcaml.
</p>

